rows.label: qst101806_msg001
rows.name: Temp implementation of LIST_QST101806

rows.label: qst101806_msg002
rows.name: I'm in a lot of debt.

rows.label: qst101806_msg003
rows.name: I thought I was going to die soon.

rows.label: qst101806_msg004
rows.name: That's ridiculous, mo.

rows.label: qst101806_msg005
rows.name:
I want to chase after the
escaped Jizo. Take me with you.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0001
rows.name:
Gamettse-baasan! My
Driver has returned.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0002
rows.name: Oh...

rows.label: qst101806_msg0003
rows.name:
Thank you for taking
care of my Vahsah, mo.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0004
rows.name:
I will repay the money
you borrowed, mo.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0005
rows.name: Oh, my... You'll pay me back?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0006
rows.name: Yes, mo!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0007
rows.name: 5000G should be enough, mo?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0008
rows.name: 5000G? Hehe! That's not nearly enough.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0009
rows.name:
Huh? What? Vahsah, how
much did you borrow, mo?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0010
rows.name:
Um... Come to think of
it, I didn't tell you.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0012
rows.name:
Fif... one, ten, a hundred, a
thousand... Five hundred thousand~~?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0013
rows.name: A lump sum cash payment... or...

rows.label: qst101806_msg0014
rows.name:
if you bring me one Ars Quartz,
I'll write off the debt.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0015
rows.name: Ars Quartz... What's that?

rows.label: qst101806_msg0016
rows.name:
It's a gem that's very rarely
salvaged in Avaritia, mo...

rows.label: qst101806_msg0017
rows.name:
For Jizo to get one is a
dream within a dream, mo.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0018
rows.name:
If you can't, then just turn that
Blade into a Core Crystal for me.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0019
rows.name:
If I sell it in Superbia,
it'll fetch a good price...

rows.label: qst101806_msg0020
rows.name: I can't do that, mo!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0021
rows.name:
Until Jizo dies, Vahsah
is Jizo's Blade, mo!

rows.label: qst101806_msg0022
rows.name:
I don't want to turn her
into a Core Crystal, mo~

rows.label: qst101806_msg0023
rows.name:
It can't be helped, Jizo.
To repay the debt...

rows.label: qst101806_msg0024
rows.name:
Hmm, this is bad... I guess we
have no choice but to die.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0025
rows.name:
Oh my, my... Hehe! What
kind-hearted companions you have.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0026
rows.name: 500,000G or an Ars Quartz...

rows.label: qst101806_msg0027
rows.name:
I don't care which, as long
as you repay the debt.

rows.label: qst101806_msg0028
rows.name: Thank you, mo... I'm sorry, mo...
